Description: C++ based Debug adapter library that implements Debug adapter protocol
(https://microsoft.github.io/debug-adapter-protocol/).
This protocol is used by IDE's to integrate with debuggers.
Revision is from `git merge-base JIRI_HEAD origin/upstream/main`.
Usage: Development use, for adding debug adapter support to zxdb.
